  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn to bend acidic substances to you will, molding and manipulating them like puppets on a string.</p><p>All creatures within 15 feet of you who are under the effects of the corroded condition has their condition ended, as you collect all of the left-over acid into a ball above your head. The ball floats for up to 1 minute or until used.</p><p>The next time you would cast a jutsu that would deal acid damage you can spend the ball of acid, upcasting the jutsu by 1 rank at no cost, ignoring upcasting limitations.</p>",
